            "briefSummary": "This is a prospective, homebased, interventional clinical study containing 10 subjects who will be enrolled. Approximately 10 (10) subjects with active anxiety and depression symptoms will receive treatment using the NeuroGlove.",
            "detailedDescription": "This is a prospective, homebased, interventional clinical study containing 10 subjects who will be enrolled. Approximately 10 (10) subjects with active anxiety and depression symptoms will receive treatment using the NeuroGlove.\n\nSubjects will be recruited in from the community. Inclusion in the study will not impact the care management of the subject. Informed consent will be obtained from all subjects before inclusion in the study."
